### Pay Tuition For Fall 2020 here

Registration Fees

You can register your student for classes by clicking here

Also, if you wish to further support St. Croix Ballet during these trying times, this can be done here as well. Any level of support is greatly appreciated.

- Registration fee - $25 Per Child - One time per year
- No Additional Registration fees for 3rd Child or more
- Performance/Snack Fee (Nutcracker/Spring Show) - $50

- Level 1-1 through 1-6 $130 USD
- Level 1-6+ 2x per week $325 USD
- Level 1-6+ 3x per week $400 USD
